data.title: Cola Duke Golf Classic By 13 Shots
data.meta_description: Oct. 18,  2004      DURHAM, N.C. -  The Blue Devils set a new tournament record at the Coca-Cola Duke Golf Classic, posting a four-under-par 860 to win the event
